                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">FDA CLEARED: HOME USE (2070)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">ICC OFF-WORLD MEDICAL AUTHORITY</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">COLONIAL MEDICAL STANDARDS BOARD</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">USCM FIELD MEDICAL EQUIPMENT CERTIFICATION</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs">&gt;</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase">ISO 13485 MEDICAL DEVICE QMS</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-4 uppercase">TRAINING & CERTIFICATION</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">OPERATOR CERTIFICATION</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">16-HOUR PROGRAM. SYSTEM OPERATION, PATIENT PREPARATION, EMERGENCY PROTOCOLS. REQUIRED FOR ALL INSTALLATIONS.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">MEDICAL STAFF TRAINING</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">40-HOUR PROGRAM. ADVANCED PROCEDURE MANAGEMENT, AI INTERACTION, MANUAL OVERRIDE PROTOCOLS.</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">SERVICE TECHNICIAN</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">80-HOUR PROGRAM. HARDWARE MAINTENANCE, SOFTWARE DIAGNOSTICS, ROBOTIC ARM CALIBRATION, CONSUMABLES MANAGEMENT.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-6">
              <h3 class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] mb-4 uppercase">SUPPORT PACKAGES</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">STANDARD</div>
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">3-YEAR WARRANTY. ANNUAL SERVICE. SOFTWARE UPDATES. CONSUMABLE RESUPPLY.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">PREMIUM</div>
